INSERT Articles ( Title, UrlSlug, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId, SiteId, Language ) VALUES ( N'Acne Paper', N'acne-paper', N'Acne Paper was a renowned bi-annual culture magazine that served as the publishing arm of Acne Studios (Ambition to Create Novel Expression), a Stockholm-based creative collective and fashion label. The magazine was founded in 2005 and remained active until 2014.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + '' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Acne Paper aimed to transcend the boundaries of a traditional fashion magazine by exploring a wide range of cultural topics beyond fashion alone. It delved into art, photography, design, architecture, literature, and other creative disciplines, presenting a holistic view of contemporary culture.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + '' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'The magazine''s editorial content was known for its high-quality writing, artistic photography, and innovative design. Each issue of Acne Paper revolved around a specific theme, which provided a cohesive narrative and allowed for a deeper exploration of the chosen subject matter.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + '' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Acne Paper featured in-depth interviews with prominent artists, designers, and creative thinkers, offering insights into their work, inspirations, and perspectives on the creative process. The magazine also showcased portfolios of exceptional photography and commissioned original art and illustrations.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + '' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'One of the notable aspects of Acne Paper was its focus on long-form articles and in-depth essays, providing readers with thoughtful and thought-provoking content. It sought to foster a deep engagement with culture, encouraging readers to ponder the larger significance of art, fashion, and creativity in society.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + '' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'The magazine''s design was equally important, with each issue displaying a meticulous attention to detail and a distinctive aesthetic. 