INSERT Articles ( Title, UrlSlug, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId, SiteId, Language ) VALUES ( N'The New York Times Magazine', N'the-new-york-times-magazine', N'The New York Times Magazine is a prestigious Sunday magazine supplement that accompanies the Sunday edition of The New York Times, one of the most prominent and widely read newspapers in the United States. It has a rich history and is known for its in-depth journalism, compelling features, and comprehensive coverage of a wide range of topics.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + '' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'The magazine was first published in 1896 as a separate publication but later became a supplement to The New York Times on Sundays. Over the years, it has evolved into a highly respected and influential publication in its own right. The New York Times Magazine has received numerous accolades for its journalism, writing, photography, and design.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + '' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'The magazine covers a diverse range of subjects, including politics, current events, culture, arts, science, technology, business, fashion, and more. It features in-depth investigative reports, long-form articles, profiles of notable individuals, essays, opinion pieces, and photo essays. The magazine often takes an in-depth and analytical approach to its stories, providing readers with comprehensive and nuanced coverage of important issues and topics.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + '' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'The New York Times Magazine has been at the forefront of groundbreaking journalism, breaking significant stories and uncovering important societal issues. It has been recognized for its exceptional investigative reporting, which has led to impactful social and political changes.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + '' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'The magazine has also gained a reputation for its visually striking and thought-provoking photography. It features photo essays and images that capture powerful moments, convey emotions,