INSERT Articles ( Title, UrlSlug, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId, SiteId, Language ) VALUES ( N'Car & Driver', N'car-and-driver', N'Car and Driver (CD or C/D) is a prominent American automotive enthusiast magazine known for its comprehensive coverage of cars, automotive news, and road tests. It has a long and rich history, beginning with its founding in the mid-20th century.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Car and Driver traces its origins back to the year 1955 when it was established as Sports Cars Illustrated. The magazine initially focused on sports cars and the emerging interest in automotive performance and enthusiast culture. Over time, Sports Cars Illustrated evolved and expanded its coverage to encompass a broader range of automotive topics.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'In 1961, the magazine underwent a name change and became Car and Driver. The new name reflected its increasing focus on covering a wider spectrum of automobiles, including mainstream cars, luxury vehicles, and performance models. Car and Driver quickly gained a reputation for its insightful and entertaining automotive journalism, attracting a dedicated readership of car enthusiasts and consumers alike.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Throughout its history, Car and Driver has provided in-depth road tests, reviews, and comparisons of new vehicles, helping readers make informed decisions about their automotive purchases. The magazine has also covered industry news, technological advancements, and trends shaping the automotive landscape. In addition to its informative content, Car and Driver has featured engaging articles, editorials, and columns that capture the excitement and passion surrounding automobiles.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Car and Driver has consistently embraced the evolving media landscape, adapting to the digital age by expanding its online presence and engaging with readers through various di